snippet.title: Cult of the Lamb | Unholy Alliance Teaser Trailer | August 12
snippet.description:
Unholy Alliance, the next FREE major update for Cult of the Lamb, is available August 12th, 2024! 🎮🧑‍🤝‍🧑

Join hands with an unlikely, corrupted ally in LOCAL CO-OP! Because friends that slay together, stay together. 

If you find yourself alone in this vast, dark plane of existence - fear not. There is much, much more in this update for you too... 😘

🙏 THE 🐐

More info to come! 
Join the flock on Discord to be the first to hear more about † UNHOLY ALLIANCE †: http://cult.link/3f4nnp7
